name: lisfun
description: The main goal of this repository is to build a reliable starter project to bootstrap a new one using a really simple Go WEB stack: [Echo](https://echo.labstack.com/)/[Ent](https://entgo.io/)/[Templ](https://templ.guide/)/[HTMX](https://htmx.org/) and everything we need to build a fancy UI like plain [Tailwindcss](https://tailwindcss.com/) or something like [daisyUI](https://daisyui.com/).
